MAJOR NELSON saved ground, gave chase nearing the three eighths pole, rounded the far turn at the rail and weakened in the lane. ELFUEGOMASBRILANTE saved ground, gave chase leaving the seven sixteenths pole, rounded the far turn at the rail and weakened. AFLEET AIRO rounded the opening turn in the six path and showed little response through the backstretch. TIZNOW TIME broke through the gate prior the start and ran loose in the post parade, rounded the opening turn about the five path, was through early and galloped the final three eighths of a mile.

GAMING JACK was carried out into the first turn and showed little response through the backstretch. SCOTTY SILVER exchanged contact with Fort fortitude leaving the gate, drifted into the first turn and never factored.

AMELIA'S DREAM came out and made contact with GREY FLAMINGO after the start then rated close at the rail the first turn, picked up the chase from the seven sixteenths pole but weakened at the rail into the far turn.
